    <div class="headline"><h2>Our camps</h2></div>
    <div class="row">
    Our Holiday Camps are designed for children aged 3-14yrs of all abilities. Players aged 5-14 can either come from 10am - 12:30pm or from 10am - 3pm, with the option of having extended hours in the morning and at end of day. 
        Tots aged 3-4 can only attend morning half day sessions.
    <br />
    Each day and session is carefully structured to provide an introduction to all the strokes in tennis, offer technical and tactical advice, and give everyone the opportunity to develop their skills in a relaxed environment. 
        </div>
    <div class="headline"><h2>How to book a camp place</h2></div>
    <div class="row md-margin-bottom-40">
        Please note that all players who participate in a holiday camp MUST either be members of the club OR pay a guest fee to the club.
        Once your camp registration is complete, the club will send you details regarding guest fee payment or membership application.
        The guest fee payable is equal to £2.00 per session.
    </div>
