            <br />
            You can select your 10 dates at the time of booking, or at a later stage, however please note that we only have a limited number of places at the camp so please book early to avoid disappointment.
            Your confirmation email will contain details of how to book any extras, including extended hours between 8:30am - 10am and between 3pm and 5pm.
